'Andreotti' is an Italian surname. Notable people with the surname include:

* Aldo Andreotti (1924–1980), mathematician
* Giulio Andreotti (1919–2013), Italian politician, former Prime Minister of
  Italy from Christian Democracy
* Lamberto Andreotti, executive
* Libero Andreotti (1875–1933)
